Package com.carrotgarden.maven.aws.cfn

Class Summary
CarrotAwsCloudForm  
CarrotAwsCloudFormCreate cloud formation: create stack based on: stack name, stack template (CarrotAwsCloudForm.stackTemplateFile), stack parameters (CarrotAwsCloudForm.stackInputParams + CarrotAwsCloudFormCreate.stackPropertiesInputFile), and produce a stack output (CarrotAwsCloudFormCreate.stackPropertiesOutputFile) ; wait for completion or fail (CarrotAwsCloudForm.stackTimeout)
CarrotAwsCloudFormDelete cloud formation: delete stack based on: stack name; ; wait for completion or fail (CarrotAwsCloudForm.stackTimeout)
